init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The aliens are not the only ones who want to know if he is still loved.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This is a story of Matt Damon, and his journey to find his place in the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt is a good sport about it all, and even helps Will Smith with his investigation.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are quite shocked, and Matt is quite shocked.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The aliens are not so thrilled.
